      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>lamb mince</strong> to the dish<strong> </strong>with<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until very lightly browned all over, breaking it up into rough, large chunks</p>",
