      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> to the dish with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, your <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, <strong>tomato paste </strong>and<strong> dried basil</strong></p><p>Add 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[850ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
