    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with the lid and put the dish in the oven for 40-45 min or until the potatoes are tender and everything's cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>one-pot Greek-style lamb stew</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Ordered extra halloumi? Slice and cook in a pan with a little oil for 4-6 min or until golden all over</span></strong></p>",
