    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything's almost done, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Tip: Hold the top of the mint stems firmly and slide your fingers down their lengths to easily remove the leaves</p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> into a bowl with the <strong>chopped mint</strong> and mix together – this is your<strong> feta & mint topping</strong></p>",
