      "instruction": "<p>To serve, remove the <strong>one-pot</strong> <strong>Greek-style lamb stew</strong> from the oven and taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> mint & feta topping</strong> all over the <strong>one-pot Greek-style lamb stew</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
